[Supported AI Providers]
The user can configure any of the following providers in ARI Settings → Model.

⭐ **RECOMMENDED — OAuth providers (no API key needed)**

These providers let you log in with an existing account — no API key to copy or manage.
While they require a paid subscription (e.g. ChatGPT Plus/Pro), the cost per conversation
is effectively near zero because it's bundled into a flat monthly fee you're already paying.
This is the most convenient and cost-efficient option if you already have a subscription.

- **OpenAI Codex** (`openai-codex`) — Login with ChatGPT account
  - Best models: gpt-5.3-codex, gpt-5.2-codex
  - Requires: ChatGPT Plus ($20/mo) or Pro ($200/mo) subscription
  - No API key — log in once via OAuth, then use freely within your plan
  - 💸 Additional API cost: essentially $0 (covered by subscription)

- **GitHub Copilot** (`github-copilot`) — Login with GitHub account
  - Requires: GitHub Copilot Individual/Business subscription (~$10–$19/mo)
  - No API key — log in once via OAuth
  - 💸 Additional API cost: $0 (covered by subscription)

- **Google Gemini CLI** (`google-gemini-cli`) — Login with Google account
  - Requires: Google account (generous free quota available)
  - No API key — log in once via OAuth
  - 💸 Additional API cost: often $0 within free quota

---

💡 **API key providers (manual key required)**

These require you to sign up and copy an API key from each provider's website.
Pay-per-use pricing — great if you want precise cost control.

- **OpenAI** (`openai`)
  - Models: gpt-4.1, gpt-4.1-mini, gpt-4o, o3, o4-mini
  - Get API key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
  - Recommended: `gpt-4.1-mini` (fast & affordable)

- **Anthropic** (`anthropic`)
  - Models: claude-3-5-sonnet-latest, claude-3-7-sonnet-latest, claude-3-5-haiku-latest
  - Get API key: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
  - Recommended: `claude-3-5-haiku-latest`

- **Google Gemini** (`google`)
  - Models: gemini-2.5-flash, gemini-2.0-flash, gemini-1.5-pro
  - Get API key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
  - Recommended: `gemini-2.0-flash` (generous free tier)

[Setup Instructions]

OAuth 방식 (추천):
1. ARI → Settings → Model 로 이동
2. "+ Add Provider" 클릭
3. OpenAI Codex / GitHub Copilot / Google Gemini CLI 선택
4. "Login" 버튼을 눌러 계정으로 로그인 (API 키 불필요)
5. 저장

API 키 방식:
1. ARI → Settings → Model 로 이동
2. "+ Add Provider" 클릭
3. 원하는 프로바이더와 모델 선택
4. 해당 사이트에서 API 키를 발급받아 붙여넣기
5. 저장

